				<td colspan="2"><span>I used to be in a similar boat (got a stay at home job now - so I cant play as much lol) and eq does play ok on a slow connection so if the Lan doesnt work dont hesitate to try dialup.  
<br />

<br />
My experience is that only Courtyard provides free broadband.  Others (Hyatt I believe) will sell you a week for less that 5 days so if you are somewhere a long time you may check into that.  I also have never run into connection difficulties - however at one courtyard they did reset the system at midnight which would cause you to go LD and have to log in again.  I also play on laptops with as little as 16meg of Video ram and it works well - some areas are very laggy (zones with lots of trees are bad) but you can still enjoy the game outside those zones.
<br />
